564
00:35:31.500 --> 00:35:33.250
Great job. Great job.

565
00:35:33.333 --> 00:35:35.292
Two things wrong with your story.

566
00:35:35.958 --> 00:35:37.917
One. we know you shot yourself.

567
00:35:38.000 --> 00:35:39.750
